-<title>Procedure</title>
-<listitem>
-<simpara>Click <emphasis role="strong">Account</emphasis>.</simpara>
-<orderedlist numeration="loweralpha">
-<listitem>
-<simpara>Enter your Red Hat Customer Portal username and password details.</simpara>
